def: That which is expectorated; a salival discharge; spittle;saliva.
Destructive to, or hindering the growth of, diphtheria bacilli.-- n.
The act or process of achromatizing.
Situated in front of any transverse axis in the body of ananimal; anterior; cephalic; esp., in front, or on the anterior, orcephalic (that is, radial or tibial) side of the axis of a limb.
Anything scattered, as flowers for decoration. [Obs.] Shak.
The act of verbalizing, or the state of being verbalized.
With a crook or bend; with the hand on the hip and elbow turnedoutward. "With one arm akimbo." Irving.
